headline: Nasdaq, Inc. Stock Is Off Its Highs, Despite Strong Results - Short Put Plays Work Here
summary: Nasdaq, Inc. reported strong free cash flow and FCF margins for Q4, but NDAQ stock has dropped 14% since then. One attractive play today is shorting out-of-the-money put options with a one-month expiry period.
